  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BIM Coordinator",
  "description": "<h2>Job description</h2>\n<p><strong>Role &amp; responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>1. Maintain CDE platforms (ACC/BIM360), ensuring meticulous documentation of files.</p>\n<p>2. Assist BIM/Design Manager in timely project submissions according to milestones.</p>\n<p>3. Support BIM/Design Manager in VDC walkthrough presentations for clients/owners.</p>\n<p>4. Conduct BIM Meetings with consultants, emphasising clash detection and model issues.</p>\n<p>5. Assign tasks to modellers and vigilantly monitor the quality of their work.</p>\n<p>6. Prepare comprehensive reports on BIM issues using Excel and Navisworks.</p>\n<p>7. Be able to develop when needed detailed 3D models of various Services using Revit.</p>\n<p>8. Collaborate with architects, engineers, contractors, and stakeholders to integrate design inputs into BIM models, involving coordination, clash detection, and resolution.</p>\n<p>9. Ensure timely submission of Shop drawings.</p>\n<p>10. Ensure BIM models strictly adhere to industry standards and project requirements.</p>\n<p>11. Conduct regular quality checks on BIM models for accuracy, completeness, and compliance, minimising errors and rework during construction.</p>\n<p>12. Prepare 3D visualisations, renderings, and animations for design reviews presentations with subcontractors and clients.</p>\n<p>13. Prepare drawings submissions for consultant approval to construction.</p>\n<p>14. Extract quantities and generate material takeoffs from BIM models for cost estimation and procurement purposes.</p>\n<p>15. Facilitate communication and collaboration among project team members through the BIM model, serving as a central file for sharing information and resolving conflicts.</p>\n<p>16. Create and update BIM elements individually and through a team.</p>\n<p>17. Prepare documentations with standard templates and legends for submission.</p>\n<p>18. Maintain BIM Libraries and standards in accordance with organisational and project requirements.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Preferred candidate profile</strong></p>\n<p>Someone willing to take lead and manage a team along with contributing individually.</p>\n<p>Able to showcase past team handling experience.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
